=== 大规模服务中断 ===
* 2011年4月20日，亚马逊云计算服务出现大规模服务中断。Elastic Block Store服务“卡死”，无法完成读/写请求。经过了至少两天服务才完全恢复正常。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://aws.amazon.com/message/65648/ |title=Summary of outage occurring April 20–22, 2011 |date=2011-04-29 |access-date=2013-07-17 |archive-date=2013-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130907143711/https://aws.amazon.com/message/65648/ }}</ref>
* 2012年6月29日，多个依赖亚马逊云计算服务的网站被迫下线，起因是AWS最大的数据中心集群——弗吉尼亚州北部出现特大暴雨。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://aws.amazon.com/message/67457/ |title=Summary of the AWS Service Event in the US East Region |date=2012-07-02 |access-date=2013-07-17 |archive-date=2013-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130724051708/http://aws.amazon.com/message/67457/ }}</ref>
* 2012年10月22日，此次服务中断影响到诸如[[Reddit|Reddit]]、[[Foursquare|Foursquare]]、[[Pinterest|Pinterest]]等网站。服务中断的原因是运营数据收集程序存在内存泄漏漏洞。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://aws.amazon.com/message/680342/ |title=Summary of the October 22, 2012 AWS Service Event in the US-East Region |date= 2012-10-22 |access-date= 2013-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130905042206/https://aws.amazon.com/message/680342/ |archive-date=  2013-09-05 |url-status=dead }}</ref>
* 2021年12月24日，亚马逊云计算服务再次出现服务中断，影响到位于东北部美国的用户访问[[Netflix|Netflix]]等网站。<ref>{{cite web|last=Bishop|first=Bryan|title=Netflix streaming down on some devices due to Amazon issues|date=2012-12-24|url=https://www.theverge.com/2012/12/24/3801978/netflix-streaming-down-on-some-devices-thanks-to-amazon-issues|publisher=The Verge|access-date=2013-02-05|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725045641/https://www.theverge.com/2012/12/24/3801978/netflix-streaming-down-on-some-devices-thanks-to-amazon-issues}}</ref>AWS表示这次事故是[[Elastic_Load_Balancing|Elastic Load Balancing]]服务造成的。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://aws.amazon.com/message/680587/ |title=Summary of the December 24, 2012 Amazon ELB Service Event in the US-East Region |date=2012-12-24 |access-date=2013-07-17 |archive-date=2013-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130807032646/http://aws.amazon.com/message/680587/ }}</ref>
* 2017年2月28日，亚马逊云计算服务的弗吉尼亚北部区域出现大规模S3服务中断。大部分依赖AWS S3服务的网站会出现假死或无法载入的问题，亚马逊在五小时内表示服务已经完全恢复。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://aws.amazon.com/message/41926/|title=Summary of the Amazon S3 Service Disruption in the Northern Virginia (US-EAST-1) Region|work=amazon.com|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112002452/https://aws.amazon.com/message/41926/}}</ref>没有因为此次事故造成数据损失的报道。事故原因是在[[调试|调试]]过程中的[[人为错误|人为错误]]导致超出预期的服务器容量被移除，因此造成多米诺骨牌效应。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cnet.com/news/aws-s3-service-disruption-a-typo-blew-up-part-of-the-internet-tuesday/ |title=A typo blew up part of the internet Tuesday |publisher=CNET |date=2017-03-02 |first1=Ben Fox |last1=Rubin |access-date=2022-04-30 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112035227/https://www.cnet.com/news/aws-s3-service-disruption-a-typo-blew-up-part-of-the-internet-tuesday/ }}</ref>
* 2020年11月25日，亚马逊云计算服务的弗吉尼亚北部区域出现数小时Kinesis服务中断。其他依赖Kinesis的服务也受到影响。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Speed|first=Richard|title=AWS admits to 'severely impaired' services in US-EAST-1, can't even post updates to Service Health Dashboard|url=https://www.theregister.com/2020/11/25/aws_down/|access-date=2020-11-25|website=www.theregister.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219181712/https://www.theregister.com/2020/11/25/aws_down/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last1=Canales |first1=Katie |last2=Dean |first2=Grace |title=Amazon Web Services is back up after a massive outage that hit sites including Roku, Adobe, and Target-owned Shipt |url=https://www.businessinsider.com/amazon-web-services-outage-websites-not-working-2020-11 |access-date=2020-11-26 |website=[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]] |archive-date=2020-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215145943/https://www.businessinsider.com/amazon-web-services-outage-websites-not-working-2020-11 }}</ref>
* 2021年12月7日，此次服务中断主要影响美国东部，造成快递服务、流媒体和诸如[[Ticketmaster|Ticketmaster]]、[[羅賓漢_(公司)|罗宾汉市场]]和[[Coinbase|Coinbase]]等服务受到影响。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/12/07/amazon-web-services-outage-causes-issues-at-disney-netflix-coinbase.html|title=Amazon Web Services outage brings some delivery operations to a standstill|last=Palmer|first=Annie|work=[[CNBC|CNBC]]|date=2021-12-07|access-date=2021-12-09|archive-date=2022-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220521123937/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/12/07/amazon-web-services-outage-causes-issues-at-disney-netflix-coinbase.html}}</ref>

== 爭議 ==
AWS於2015年基於[[Elasticsearch|Elasticsearch]]推出自己的服務，並將其稱為Amazon Elasticsearch Service。隨後AWS和Elasticsearch就[[商標|商標]]和[[代碼開源|代碼開源]]上發生了激烈的爭議<ref>{{Cite web|title=AWS被指「露天開採」開源軟體，Amazon：因應客戶要求|url=https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/134923|access-date=2022-02-27|work=iThome|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2022-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220228012546/https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/134923|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最終雙方達成[[和解|和解]]，Amazon Elasticsearch Service改名為Elastic Cloud，AWS則成為了Elasticsearch的合作夥伴<ref>{{Cite web|title=Elastic和AWS不吵了，不只在侵權訴訟達成協議還進一步深化合作|url=https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/149430|access-date=2022-02-27|work=iThome|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2022-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220309131934/https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/149430|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Elastic 与亚马逊达成和解：“只有一个 Elasticsearch”_Cloud_诉讼_Amazon|url=https://m.sohu.com/a/524486051_355140/m.sohu.com/a/524486051_355140|access-date=2022-02-27|work=m.sohu.com|language=en}}</ref>。

